data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. BRAND NEW ROOF! This beautiful 10 acre homestead is located in one of the most desirable areas of High Springs. This gorgeous property is primarily cleared with lush, green grass ready for your farm animals or for your kids to run and play. There are granddaddy oak trees on 3 sides of the property creating a beautiful barrier from neighboring properties. The home sits on the back of the property with a long scenic drive as you approach. You're greeted by a wood deck front porch perfect for rocking chairs to enjoy sunrise and sunset. When you enter the home you'll love the abundance of light and soaring 2 story cathedral ceilings. The unique layout of this home was designed to accentuate the beauty of the outdoors, with mirrored French doors on the front and back of the home and doors on each side of the home as well. The warm wood floors and abundance of natural light make you feel right at home. You'll appreciate the French country style galley kitchen with a cozy breakfast nook surrounded by windows. The main floor boasts a large primary bedroom with a large walk-in closet that connects to the laundry room, a full bath, two additional guest bedrooms, and an oversized pantry. The second story boasts a loft flex space at the top of the staircase that overlooks the living room as well as the back of the home, a spacious guest bedroom, and a full bathroom. Additional features include: a rear and side porch, a full garden, and a fire pit surrounded by granddaddy oak trees. Don't miss your opportunity to own this quaint home and beautiful property! **Buyer to verify all property details.**
